Liam’s selfishness led him to commit a crime against the Prince several years ago. He’s gotten away with it until now, but the Prince has methods to force a confession.Prince Briar says he doesn’t want a thoughtless toy that feels nothing, but his actions prove otherwise. Every punishment and lesson is designed to chip off a little more and turn Liam into a shell that only obeys and serves.Escape is the only option if he wants to keep any part of himself.